，每股发售97美元，如此计算，其估值或达到1800亿美元；第三是印度最大的零售连锁店信实零售（Reliance Retail），估值达到1008亿美元。 而AI领域中，被称为OpenAI最大对手的Anthropic估值仅184亿美元，Anthropic目前也在洽谈新融资。 以企业分析平台CB Insights的数据判断，1000亿美元的估值将把OpenAI推向美国第二高估值的初创公司宝座，仅次于SpaceX。硅谷“造神” OpenAI拟开展新一轮融资 估值不低于千亿美元"},"attached_info":"CkAIgLflmZO2jNUtEAMaCTEwMzY2OTQ1NSC8xZmsBjAAOLYBQCZyCTYzNjI1OTQyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"3.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f5d5a4632f3cd4a3baf1ce9757241903_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1703402060.213650","card_id":"Q_436192830","target":{"id":436192830,"title":"孩子的自律真的要靠家长逼出来吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/436192830","type":"question","created":1608728078,"answer_count":2800,"follower_count":14386,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1000,2146,24166,170023],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"是应该严管严监督还是应该顺其自然？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IgLflmZO2jNUtEAMaCDU5MjEwNjU5II78jP8FMAA4snBAJ3IJNDM2MTkyODMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"3.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2eb83d890c0711fe3fa722596c191024_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1703402060.214014","card_id":"Q_636189838","target":{"id":636189838,"title":"可以说说你的2023年待办清单完成进度吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/636189838","type":"question","created":1703253934,"answer_count":106,"follower_count":150,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[38009,1913537,3163646,3185992,3200010],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2023进入倒计时，你的待办清单都完成了吗？"},"attached_info":"CkAIgLflmZO2jNUtEAMaCTEwMzY1Mzk2MyCur5asBjAAOJYBQChyCTYzNj